Prof. Andrews is one of the most dedicated profs I've had. She is a much respected political scientist. Her love of her craft is quite visible. I wish she would run for office as I find her credible and capable of critically dismantling the problems of governance facing this country. If you take her class, you will discover her quiet brilliance!

She seems like she such a kind heart, and she's brilliant, too. She has an incredibly good reputation in Ottawa. Try visiting her in her office hours - she always makes time for students, even though she's really busy.
